        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-[#f0f0f5] mb-1.5">Account SID <span class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] text-xs">(ACxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx)</span></label>
